    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月のテンペストのライブ数日前",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ月ストのライブ当日か\nまさか、麻奈の誕生日にライブとはなぁ",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、あの時のバースデーライブと同じ会場だなんて\nあいつが知ったら、なんて言うかな……",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっちろん、私もゲストで出るからね！",
      "startTime": 18.0029246409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "全世界がずっと待ってた姉妹共演だもん",
      "startTime": 21.7562601169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言いそうだよなぁ\nまぁ、今回はゲストとして、遙子さんが出るんだが",
      "startTime": 28.9333344778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈の誕生日に――\n琴乃のライブに、遙子さんが出るのか……",
      "startTime": 35.9000011445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "startTime": 40.759594218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "会場、押さえられたって本当！？",
      "startTime": 42.7929260969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、本当だ\n今年は出来るぞ、長瀬麻奈バースデーライブ",
      "startTime": 47.6666678112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　ありがとう{user}くん！",
      "startTime": 51.5338566382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thank-01.m4a",
      "text": "もう、去年からずーっとずーーっと……",
      "startTime": 55.2338578302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-04.m4a",
      "text": "ずーーーーっと、やりたかったから、嬉しい！",
      "startTime": 59.9338594356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本当に出来るんだぁ、バースデーライブ……",
      "startTime": 64.3405267378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにやりたかったのか？　デビューしてまだ一年と\n少しだし、誕生日とはいえ大がかりなことは出来ないぞ",
      "startTime": 71.6333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-08.m4a",
      "text": "チッチッチ！　分かってないね",
      "startTime": 76.2927039382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "去年、私がどれだけ歯がゆい思いをしたかを",
      "startTime": 79.6527055583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-03.m4a",
      "text": "たまたま私の誕生日にライブがあったけど",
      "startTime": 84.2260423578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも通りの普通のライブだったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 87.4527004636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "スタッフさん達がケーキを運んで来てくれて",
      "startTime": 90.9260367629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "私もそれでようやく誕生日だって思い出したくらいでさ",
      "startTime": 94.2260368477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-11.m4a",
      "text": "会場のファンのみんなも、一緒になって",
      "startTime": 98.2260367629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お祝いしてくれて、凄く嬉しかったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 102.1333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-02.m4a",
      "text": "この麻奈ちゃんの誕生日だよ！？　ほんとはみんな",
      "startTime": 106.392717671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もーっと気合いを入れてお祝いしたかったはず！",
      "startTime": 110.3793879956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういうものか……？",
      "startTime": 114.5260535475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "そういうものだよ！　私だって、今まで応援してくれた",
      "startTime": 117.3918810284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなに、しっかり感謝を伝えたいし",
      "startTime": 122.1252184988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "誕生日って、私だけじゃなくて",
      "startTime": 125.5585431173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれてる人達にとっても特別なはずだもん",
      "startTime": 128.5852163312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だからね！　今年は絶対絶対",
      "startTime": 132.9585548158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-15.m4a",
      "text": "バースデーライブがやりたかったの！",
      "startTime": 136.2918763793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。麻奈にとっても、ファンの人達にとっても\n日頃の感謝を伝えられる、特別な一日ってことか",
      "startTime": 144.1666790009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（そしてそれは、俺達星見プロみんなの思いでもある）\n（今年は最高のステージを麻奈に贈るんだ）",
      "startTime": 153.4000123342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（そのために、三枝さんと遙子さんと俺の三人で）\n（麻奈へのサプライズ企画を進めているしな）",
      "startTime": 161.0666790009,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、{user}くん",
      "startTime": 164.1415317613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうと決まれば、最高のバースデーライブにするために",
      "startTime": 166.2415317613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-04.m4a",
      "text": "――企画百本ノック、始めるよ！",
      "startTime": 170.57487425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-05.m4a",
      "text": "バッチこーい！",
      "startTime": 173.4415215369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "テンション高いなぁ……\nまぁ、麻奈の気合いの理由は、よく分かったよ",
      "startTime": 178.2333497365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_52_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-26.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今は忙しい？　じゃあ明日？　明後日？　三日後？",
      "startTime": 181.9280666111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
